<br>
These sorts of characters *are* appearing in experience groups, and players notice the difference another tank makes versus a wizard. Note that I have done the above, and it wasn't very hard.  Note also that because of all the time I'd played the game on Povar, I had a much better idea about which weapons to get and how much to pay for them, etc.<br>
